{"title_page": "I'm Outstanding", "text_new": "{{1990s-single-stub}}\n{{Infobox song\n| name       = I'm Outstanding\n| cover      = Im Outstanding.jpg\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Shaquille O'Neal]]\n| album      = [[Shaq Diesel]]\n| B-side     = Ode to Shaquille\n| released   = November 10, 1993\n| format     = [[Gramophone record|Vinyl]], [[CD single|CD]]\n| recorded   = 1993\n| studio     =\n| venue      =\n| genre      = [[Hip hop music|Hip hop]]\n| length     = 4:07\n| label      = [[Jive Records|Jive]]\n| writer     = O'Neal<br> Alisa Yarbrough <br> Erick Sermon <br> Raymound Calhoun\n| producer   = [[Erick Sermon]]\n| chronology = [[Shaquille O'Neal]]\n| prev_title = [[(I Know I Got) Skillz]]\n| prev_year  = 1993\n| next_title = [[Shoot Pass Slam]]\n| next_year  = 1994\n}}\n\"'''I'm Outstanding'''\" is the second single released from [[Shaquille O'Neal]]'s debut album, ''[[Shaq Diesel]]'' (1993). Produced by [[Erick Sermon]], the single was a minor success, making it to 47 on the [[Billboard Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/shaquille-oneal|title=Shaquille O'Neal|website=Billboard|access-date=2020-04-21}}</ref>\n\n== Samples ==\n\"I'm Outstanding\" sampled the following songs:\n*\"[[Don't Stop the Music (Yarbrough and Peoples song)|Don't Stop the Music]]\" by [[Yarbrough & Peoples]]\n*\"[[The Payback (song)|The Payback]]\" by [[James Brown]]\n*\"[[Outstanding]]\" by [[The Gap Band]]\n*\"[[Jingling Baby]]\" by [[LL Cool J]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.whosampled.com/sample/view/11812/Shaquille%20O'Neal-I'm%20Outstanding_James%20Brown-The%20Payback/ |title=Shaquille O&#39;Neal&#39;s I&#39;m Outstanding sample of James Brown&#39;s The Payback - WhoSampled |publisher=Whosampled.com |date= |accessdate=October 19, 2010}}</ref>\n\n==Single track listing==\n\n===A-side===\n#\"I'm Outstanding\" ([[LP record|LP]] version) \u2013 4:07\n#\"I'm Outstanding\" (Funk Lord remix) \u2013 3:55\n\n=